    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（如果这些孩子里，有人能够读取人心……）"
  },
  "003251": {
    "context": "003251",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（他们之所以会躲着我们……说不定就是因为我们几个里，有人对他们抱有恶意……！）"
  },
  "003256": {
    "context": "003256",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "简直难以置信——但这样一切都能解释通了。"
  },
  "003261": {
    "context": "003261",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "——那么，抱有恶意的是谁？"
  },
  "003266": {
    "context": "003266",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "首先，可以确定渡濑不是。这一点他自己很清楚。"
  },
  "003272": {
    "context": "003272",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（那也就是说，是在另外四个人里……？）"
  },
  "003277": {
    "context": "003277",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "一旦产生这样的想法，便不禁觉得每个人都可疑了起来。"
  },
  "003282": {
    "context": "003282",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "心里的不安迅速膨胀着，心跳也越来越快。"
  },
  "003287": {
    "context": "003287",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "怀疑招致着新的怀疑——甚至很快又掉转了枪口："
  },
  "003293": {
    "context": "003293",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（不对……或许，正相反？）"
  },
  "003299": {
    "context": "003299",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（如果抱有恶意的，反而是他们几个孩子呢？）"
  },
  "003304": {
    "context": "003304",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "能够读取人心的几个孩子，出于某种动机，要把渡濑他们逼至绝境。"
  },
  "003309": {
    "context": "003309",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "这或许是荒诞不经的臆想，但——"
  },
  "003315": {
    "context": "003315",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（如果真是这样的话……他们几个，我们对付得来吗……？）"
  },
  "003320": {
    "context": "003320",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "刚一想到这里，"
  },
  "003421": {
    "context": "003421",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "「！」"
  },
  "003426": {
    "context": "003426",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "突如其来的头痛，让渡濑叫了出来。"
  },
  "003437": {
    "context": "003437",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "「啊……呜……！」"
  },
  "003442": {
    "context": "003442",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "头晕得厉害，意识也越飘越远。"
  },
  "003453": {
    "context": "003453",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "（糟……糟了……！）"
  },
  "003510": {
    "context": "003510",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "渡濑跌跌撞撞地，跑出了资料室。"
  },
  "003516": {
    "context": "003516",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "惠那吓了一跳，连忙问道："
  },
  "003552": {
    "context": "003552",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "恵那",
    "string": "「怎么了，队长？！」"
  },
  "003563": {
    "context": "003563",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "「不，没……突然觉得难受……！」"
  },
  "003592": {
    "context": "003592",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "恵那",
    "string": "「诶？！没事吧？！」"
  },
  "003603": {
    "context": "003603",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "「抱，抱歉……去一下厕所……！」"
  },
  "003614": {
    "context": "003614",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "「老师你就先待在这里……！」"
  },
  "003643": {
    "context": "003643",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "恵那",
    "string": "「等，等一下，队长？！」"
  },
  "003698": {
    "context": "003698",
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "",
    "string": "惠那关切地问道，但渡濑已然冲出了资料室。"
  },
  "003711": {
    "context": "003711",
    "code": "0x02",
    "string": "@ignore"
  }
